com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.node

Class ArrayNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode
      • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.node.BaseJsonNode
        • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.node.ContainerNode<ArrayNode>
          • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.node.ArrayNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeNode, JsonSerializable, Iterable<JsonNode>

    public final class ArrayNode
extends ContainerNode<ArrayNode>
    Override of Jackson's ArrayNode

    We override it to make it final (the original implementation isn't), which also allows for code simplification all around.
